org.neo4j.graphdb
Interface Expander

All Superinterfaces:
RelationshipExpander
All Known Implementing Classes:
OrderedByTypeExpander, StandardExpander
public interface Expander
extends RelationshipExpander

This interface is an extension of the RelationshipExpander interface that makes it possible to build customized versions of an Expander.

Method Detail

reversed

Expander reversed()
Description copied from interface: RelationshipExpander
Returns a new instance with the exact expansion logic, but reversed. For example if this expander is set to expand:
  • KNOWS : OUTGOING
  • LIVES : INCOMING
Then the reversed expander will be set to expand:
  • KNOWS : INCOMING
  • LIVES : OUTGOING

Specified by:
reversed in interface RelationshipExpander
Returns:
a reversed RelationshipExpander.
